title: Cops describe "smell of death" but did "loving daughter" brutally murder her own dad and 6-year-old-daughter?
itunes:title: Cops describe "smell of death" but did "loving daughter" brutally murder her own dad and 6-year-old-daughter?
description:
Cheyenne Jessie reports her father and 6 year-old daughter missing. Responding police respond are overwhelmed by the rotten smell coming from the home. Joining Nancy Grace to look at the how police discovered the bodies of the pair: Judge and trial attorney Ashley Wilcott, forensics expert Joseph Scott Morgan, former New Jersey Police Detective Steve Rogers, Medical Examiner for the state of Florida Dr. Tim Gallagher, Psychoanalyst Dr Bethany Marshall and Crime Online reporter Dave Mack.
